<i>I wanna play a game.</i>

47
00:07:07,477 --> 00:07:10,382
<i>This game will take place</i>
<i>in a room not much bigger</i>

48
00:07:10,383 --> 00:07:13,588
<i>than the room you've</i>
<i>spent most of your life in.</i>

49
00:07:13,589 --> 00:07:15,326
<i>A prison cell.</i>

50
00:07:15,327 --> 00:07:17,864
<i>Despite all of the
advantages and privileges</i>

51
00:07:17,865 --> 00:07:19,567
<i>that you were given</i>
<i>at birth,</i>

52
00:07:19,568 --> 00:07:22,941
<i>you have returned</i>
<i>to prison again and again.</i>

53
00:07:22,942 --> 00:07:26,348
<i>More comfortable in chains</i>
<i>than you are in freedom.</i>

54
00:07:26,349 --> 00:07:29,989
<i>Tonight we will see how</i>
<i>far you are willing to go</i>

55
00:07:29,990 --> 00:07:33,462
<i>to break those chains</i>
<i>once and for all.</i>

56
00:07:33,463 --> 00:07:35,099
<i>Live or die, Troy.</i>

57
00:07:35,100 --> 00:07:37,203
<i>Make your choice.</i>

58
