71
00:09:32,067 --> 00:09:33,970
[screaming]

72
00:09:33,971 --> 00:09:35,739
Fuck! Fuck! Oohh!

73
00:09:41,953 --> 00:09:43,923
[screaming]

74
00:09:53,142 --> 00:09:56,481
[Kerry] I really had this feeling
it was going to be him.

75
00:09:56,482 --> 00:09:59,687
Kerry, Eric is
a missing persons case,

76
00:09:59,688 --> 00:10:01,224
not a homicide case.

77
00:10:02,995 --> 00:10:07,236
