than 30 feet out that door

505
00:50:30,849 --> 00:50:32,952
without the collar
detonating.

506
00:50:32,953 --> 00:50:36,526
Or you could try and take
the collar off yourself.

507
00:50:36,527 --> 00:50:37,895
