in the wrong place

509
00:50:39,867 --> 00:50:41,402
could trigger it.

510
00:50:41,403 --> 00:50:42,370
I should know.

511
00:50:46,012 --> 00:50:46,947
I built it.

512
00:50:50,822 --> 00:50:55,129
So. Do you have
everything you need?

513
00:50:56,567 --> 00:50:58,837
