to cut someone open.

514
00:50:58,838 --> 00:51:02,745
I don't have the tools
to save a life.

515
00:51:02,746 --> 00:51:05,517
You'd be surprised
what tools can save a life.

516
00:51:52,579 --> 00:51:54,682
<i>[Jigsaw]</i>
<i>Hello, Amanda.</i>

517
00:51:54,683 --> 00:51:58,222
<i>You don't know me,</i>
