518
00:52:00,127 --> 00:52:01,630
<i>I want to play a game.</i>

519
00:52:01,631 --> 00:52:04,001
[gasping]

520
00:52:04,002 --> 00:52:06,906
<i>There is only one chance</i>
<i>to open the device.</i>

521
00:52:11,483 --> 00:52:13,386
<i>In the stomach</i>
<i>of your dead cellmate.</i>

522
00:52:18,865 --> 00:52:20,099
<i>Look around, Amanda.</i>

523
00:52:20,100 --> 00:52:23,540
<i>Know that I'm not playing.</i>

524
00:52:23,541 --> 00:52:25,544
<i>Live or die.</i>

525
00:52:25,545 --> 00:52:27,414
<i>Make your choice.</i>

526
00:52:32,726 --> 00:52:34,061
