527
00:52:34,062 --> 00:52:35,229
<i>Congratulations.</i>

528
00:52:35,230 --> 00:52:37,200
<i>You are still alive.</i>

529
00:52:37,201 --> 00:52:42,511
<i>Most people are so
ungrateful to be alive,</i>

530
00:52:42,512 --> 00:52:46,285
<i>but not you,</i>
<i>not anymore.</i>

531
00:52:46,286 --> 00:52:50,694
Amanda,
do not be afraid.

532
00:52:50,695 --> 00:52:52,732
<i>Your life has just begun.</i>

533
00:53:10,735 --> 00:53:13,139
He made it through
the freezer room.

534
00:53:16,514 --> 00:53:18,115
