554
00:56:11,497 --> 00:56:12,898
[thumping]

555
00:56:25,424 --> 00:56:27,427
[Man]
Hello?

556
00:56:27,428 --> 00:56:29,197
Help me, please!

557
00:56:33,273 --> 00:56:35,777
Please, help me!

558
00:56:35,778 --> 00:56:38,115
[coughing]

559
00:56:38,116 --> 00:56:40,453
I'm in here!

560
00:56:40,454 --> 00:56:42,791
[coughing continues]

561
00:56:42,792 --> 00:56:45,631
Please get me
