[gagging]

564
00:56:51,777 --> 00:56:52,945
Hello?

565
00:56:52,946 --> 00:56:54,782
[coughing]

566
00:56:54,783 --> 00:56:55,784
I know you're there.

567
00:56:55,785 --> 00:56:58,490
Please!
Please help me!

568
00:57:02,131 --> 00:57:06,138
