Please, answer me!

569
00:57:06,139 --> 00:57:07,574
Help me!

570
00:57:10,147 --> 00:57:12,317
Please!

571
00:57:12,318 --> 00:57:13,586
Help me.

572
00:57:16,994 --> 00:57:18,830
Get me out of here, please.

573
00:57:18,831 --> 00:57:19,999
Please help me.

574
00:57:20,000 --> 00:57:21,469
Get me out of here!

575
00:57:21,470 --> 00:57:22,738
Please!

576
00:57:23,941 --> 00:57:25,109
Don't just stand there!

577
00:57:25,110 --> 00:57:26,646
Help me!

578
00:57:26,647 --> 00:57:28,984
[Man grunts]

579
00:57:28,985 --> 00:57:30,754
<i>[static]</i>

580
00:57:30,755 --> 00:57:34,327
<i>[Jigsaw] Jeff, when the judge</i>
<i>presiding over your case</i>

581
00:57:34,328 --> 00:57:37,835
<i>sentenced your boy's</i>
<i>murderer so lightly,</i>

582
00:57:37,836 --> 00:57:39,905
<i>your soul</i>
<i>never recovered.</i>

583
00:57:39,906 --> 00:57:44,381
<i>Now you have the power to sentence
his soul straight to Hell.</i>

584
00:57:44,382 --> 00:57:46,686
<i>Or you can forgive.</i>

585
00:57:46,687 --> 00:57:51,696
<i>The key that will free him is hidden
inside your son's possessions--</i>

586
00:57:51,697 --> 00:57:55,136
<i>possessions you have clung to</i>
<i>for far too long.</i>

587
00:57:55,137 --> 00:57:59,845
<i>Now, if you flip the switch on
the incinerator underneath you,</i>

588
00:57:59,846 --> 00:58:02,317
<i>the fire will cleanse you</i>
<i>of this obsession</i>

589
00:58:02,318 --> 00:58:04,020
<i>and destroy them all,</i>

590
00:58:04,021 --> 00:58:06,693
<i>leaving only</i>
<i>the key remaining.</i>

591
00:58:06,694 --> 00:58:08,697
<i>It is also the key</i>
<i>that will bring you closer</i>

592
00:58:08,698 --> 00:58:12,370
<i>to the man accountable</i>
<i>for taking your child.</i>

593
00:58:12,371 --> 00:58:14,709
<i>He doesn't</i>
<i>have much time, Jeff.</i>

594
00:58:14,710 --> 00:58:15,744
<i>Let the game begin.</i>

595
00:58:15,745 --> 00:58:16,746
[Man] Please,
get me out of here.

596
00:58:16,747 --> 00:58:18,282
Please!

597
00:58:19,853 --> 00:58:22,223
[whirring and clanking]

598
00:58:22,224 --> 00:58:23,827
What is that?

599
00:58:30,040 --> 00:58:31,108
What's that sound?

600
00:58:32,311 --> 00:58:34,280
[Man]
What are you doing?

601
00:59:07,181 --> 00:59:09,852
[Man coughing
and sputtering]

602
00:59:09,853 --> 00:59:13,425
